data.description: Parse and generate Cisco configuration files
data.PS: The following links are only valid for module list maintainers:
data.rationale:
Cisco::Conf was already taken.

    Cisco::Config isn't right 'cause this generally isn't used to
    create a new configuration but rather to manipulate an existing one.

    Cisco::Parse isn't right 'cause it does more than parse, it
    manipulates.

    Cisco::Reconfig felt right.
